<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #ffc107; color: #856404; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9f9f9; }
        .status { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; margin: 15px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Loan Application Under Review</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello <%= firstName %>,</h2>
            <p>Great news! Your upfront payment has been verified and your loan application is now under review.</p>
            
            <div class="status">
                <h3>Application Status</h3>
                <p><strong>Application ID:</strong> <%= loanId %></p>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color: #ffc107; font-weight: bold;">Under Review</span></p>
                <p><strong>Payment Verified:</strong> ✅ Yes</p>
                <p><strong>Payment Amount:</strong> ₦<%= paymentAmount.toLocaleString() %></p>
                <p><strong>Verification Date:</strong> <%= verificationDate %></p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Our team will review your application and documents</li>
                <li>We may contact you if additional information is needed</li>
                <li>You'll receive a decision within 2-3 business days</li>
                <li>We'll notify you immediately once a decision is made</li>
            </ul>

            <p>You can check your application status anytime in your dashboard.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>First International Financial Services Loan Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 First International Financial Services. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>